::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ozone <- read.table("../donnees/ozone_long.txt", header = T, sep = ";")
mod.lin6v <- lm(O3~T6 + T12 + Ne12 + Ne15 + Vx + O3v,data=ozone)
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(rstudent(mod.lin6v), pch = ".",ylab = "Résidus studentisés par VC")
abline(h = c(-2,2))
lines(lowess(rstudent(mod.lin6v)))
```

